text: The Kardashian family is reportedly not shocked by Blac Chyna's fist fight at Six Flags on Sunday evening, as the famous family continues their legal feud with Rob Kardashian's ex. Chyna was filmed by multiple witnesses attempting to fight someone at Six Flags Magic Mountain in Valencia, California on Easter Sunday. The videos show her swinging her children's ride - on toy car around, trying to hit someone with it. At various points in the altercation, her friends hold her back. A source close to the Kardashians told E!
